Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:04.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro and I ran into \Ncomedian DoDonPa Rokusuke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:09.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}turning himself in at the \Npolice station near Beika Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.78,Comedian,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa Rokusuke (30) \NComedian
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:14.43,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He claimed to have killed Hideki Tendo, \Nthe president of his talent agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:22.81,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,However, the police investigation \Nturned up inconsistencies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the murder weapon, time of death,\Nand contradictions in his testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:30.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When a witness to his alibi named \NIzumi Suda-san was discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.92,Artist,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Suda (68)\NArtist
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.88,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,it became clear he turned himself in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,under false pretenses to become the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:40.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa Rokusuke-san was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.73,DCMain,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.71,DCMain,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect the \Nreputation of Hideki Tendo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.36,DCMain,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I, DoDonPa Rokusuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:57.16,DCMain,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to be called his murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.05,DCMain,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What that intent, I falsely turned myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.66,DCMain,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:09.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how did you guys know \NDoDonPa-san turned himself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.75,DCMain,KIKUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.55,DCMain,KIKUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Every station received an \Nanonymous tip by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.14,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Who had that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.43,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The people who knew were...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.18,DCItalic,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:26.37,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine that policeman \Nleaked the information,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.94,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and it wasn't me or the old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:34.57,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe his goal wasn't to become the \Nculprit of a murder he didn't commit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.09,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but to make us think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:44.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The hidden lines on the palm are the fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:46.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The deduction catches fire \Non the line to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A world renowned comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:49.76,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,An unexpected remark brings \Nan alibi crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:53.19,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth with the \Nbody of a child and the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:55.59,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:41.99,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)}The Comedian Who Turned Himself In\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:40.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"The Comedian Who Turned Himself In, Part 2!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister! It's time for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.99,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:52.29,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,She left early this morning \Nfor a karate match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.88,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.08,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I have the day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:02.23,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.77,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect the \Nreputation of Hideki Tendo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:17.11,news_top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Truth Behind DoDonPa Turning Himself In \N{\fs12} "I wanted to be called his murderer."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:17.11,news bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,Press Conference Held Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.42,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I, DoDonPa Rokusuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.48,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to be called his murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.26,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What that intent, I falsely turned myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:17.11,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.65,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Things really worked out well for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:24.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,He was thrust into the spotlight, \Nand he's the man of the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:28.67,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But why did he turn himself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:33.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Watching him on TV, I thought he was \Nan unpleasant man with a strong personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:36.37,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but he's actually a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,With his sudden spike in popularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:44.59,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,he must be getting a lot of \Noffers and raking in the cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.95,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:51.60,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa never lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro asked me to check\Nout the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be really stuck on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:23.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Did the suspect use this emergency \Nstaircase to enter and exit the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.85,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:28.39,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The landlord hasn't seen anyone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.14,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He was also wondering about the metal\Npipe that was the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:37.06,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,There was a construction site \Non the way from Beika Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.02,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it was brought from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.78,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:45.65,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone spoke highly of the victim Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.15,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,They said he's not the \Ntype to extort someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.53,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:54.91,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally different from\Nwhat DoDonPa-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.41,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.54,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.96,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You received a call from the suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.36,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:10.74,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The police department just \Nreceived a call from the suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.55,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,saying Tendo had been extorting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.82,DCItalic,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo wouldn't stop extorting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.31,DCItalic,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take it anymore, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:24.10,DCItalic,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, \Nbut could you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.82,DCItalic,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.54,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,She called from a public phone, \Nand I already sent some investigators there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.45,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Based on her language, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.23,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.65,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.52,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit's a woman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.34,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.07,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.22,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might be able to \Nhelp you find the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.47,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Tendo-san won't \Nbe able to rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:59.18,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Kogoro said he already \Nknows who the true culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He said all he needed now was evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.33,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.40,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.28,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He is a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.17,DCMain,DODOPNA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:15.28,DCMain,DODOPNA,0000,0000,0000,,The Sleeping Kogoro is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:22.37,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa-san, you dropped \Nyour pachinko parlor tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.42,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.94,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand the suspect being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.36,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,She must've been easy to extort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:32.73,DCMain,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.68,DCMain,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Kogoro Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to confirm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.77,DCMain,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,He truly is a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.19,DCMain,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. It was the same every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.44,DCMain,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I even asked him why once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.45,DCItalic,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,You always come around this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.82,DCItalic,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,a little before 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:57.30,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,I have a habit of eating while watching \Nmorning programs that start at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.62,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,The female announcer is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.74,DCItalic,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.37,DCItalic,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,So you eat while watching \Nthe female announcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.44,DCMain,OKAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why he liked her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.77,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.36,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He always ate breakfast at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.21,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:20.64,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro Mouri-san sent you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.64,Studio - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1571,1)}Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:24.75,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's Kogoro Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's a famous detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.53,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:33.56,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, if he's got questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:38.41,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,tell him to come here himself \Ninstead of sending a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:43.66,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She certainly is \Ndetached from the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:48.20,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably why he used \Nher to create his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mouri-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.42,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you ask me to do this, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:03.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What point is there in talking to her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:03.85,Studio,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.73,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:15.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Suda-san, you don't pay too much \Nattention to the time, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.81,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:22.87,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Once I enter my studio, \NI don't stop painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.08,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,When I get tired, I lie down over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.75,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So, about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:38.71,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have a TV, radio, or cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:43.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,that wall clock is your only way to tell time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:44.82,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.60,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That alone is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.83,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.59,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:58.99,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I already told the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.92,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Two nights ago, DoDonPa-kun called to say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:05.05,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,he would stop by at 9:00 the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:08.24,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,and he came yesterday at exactly that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:11.77,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you confirm the time using that clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:15.13,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It was exactly \N9:00, just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:20.59,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've confirmed that, let's leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.14,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, when the police came...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.65,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.90,DCItalic,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.43,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,...it seemed like you were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always take naps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.52,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.79,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I must've been really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:47.57,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,While chatting with DoDonPa-kun \Nand eating the cake he brought,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.91,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I started to feel tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.44,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I said we're leaving, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,One more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:01.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you lock the door to the studio \Nwhen you sleep here at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.33,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.23,DCMain,IZUMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here anyone \Nwould want to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:11.31,Studio,,0000,0000,0000,,Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:15.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Her story didn't leave any room for doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.45,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.62,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.62,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.87,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Paradise Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Do the machines pay out well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:40.15,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,If they could talk, \Nthey'd be begging you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This place is up ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.72,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.30,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.05,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.75,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Were you handing out those tissues yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:53.90,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.44,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I started handing them out just \Nbefore 10:00 AM yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:02.20,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you give any to someone \Nyou recognized from TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.25,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:09.95,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.71,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he determined the \Nidentity of the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.96,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,You were called, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.83,DCMain,DONDONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:19.21,DCMain,DONDONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I received a call from \NMouri-san on my way to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.72,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. I didn't get anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.72,tendo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}Tendo Talent\NAgency
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.54,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That damn pachinko parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:27.73,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.72,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Mouri-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:34.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I heard you determined \Nthe identity of the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.90,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're the one who called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.06,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is the Sleeping \NKogoro I've heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.32,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's discuss the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:55.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,the murder of the talent \Nagency president Hideki Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:05.26,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We know a woman was being extorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.30,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:13.41,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That was a trick the suspect pulled \Nto draw attention away from himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.14,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:19.51,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The story about Tendo\Nextorting someone is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.80,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, DoDonPa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:27.18,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're the one who killed Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.95,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:33.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You did turn yourself in for his murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:38.95,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We already determined his \Nconfession was false.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.98,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:44.28,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand my desire \Nto protect Tendo-san's reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:50.22,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,even if it meant bearing the guilt \Nof a murder I didn't commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:57.31,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't feel even a shred of that desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.77,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Then why would I turn myself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:09.20,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I have an alibi for yesterday at 9:00 \Nwhen the president was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.24,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.03,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:15.25,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.66,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.59,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a vicious man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:22.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,...to manipulate a police investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:28.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday morning, \Nyou secretly came to Beika City
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,around 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:35.18,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You stole a metal pipe from \Na deserted construction site,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,hid it inside a club case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:41.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and took the emergency staircase to \Narrive at this office around 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.61,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning! It's DoDonPa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.81,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. You're early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.45,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:55.83,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,You ate breakfast this morning around \N8:00 like you always do, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.05,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.75,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.70,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:06.75,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,for when they determine the time\Nof your death during the autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.38,DCItalic,TENDO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After committing the crime, you hid \Nthe weapon behind the apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:23.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,hurried back to Akebono City, \Nand visited Suda-san's studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,...at 10:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.84,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,10:00 AM?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.40,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I visited her at 9:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.60,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.17,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Even Suda-san said it was 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:38.16,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,She was sure of the time \Nbecause she checked her clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What if that clock were \Nrunning one hour slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.79,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.12,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:48.17,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We checked for ourselves \Nwhen we went to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.16,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.67,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa-san came right at 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:16:01.18,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,He returned the clock to the correct time\Nbefore the police came to check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.92,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.16,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Two nights ago, you must have waited
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:09.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,for Suda-san to fall asleep \Nbefore breaking into her studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Suda-san, who is indifferent to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:16.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't notice if her clock \Nwere running one hour behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:20.14,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I come at the wrong time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:20.70,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:24.31,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.46,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:30.84,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You made Suda-san believe \Nyou visited her at 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:36.34,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, you put sleeping pills \Nin the cake you brought for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.39,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Suda-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.49,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.19,DCItalic,SUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly feel so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.84,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.67,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.24,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just let myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Then you returned the \Nclock to the correct time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:00.91,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the clock was showing the \Ncorrect time when I went to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:06.15,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the inspiration for \Nmy next comic monologue, Mouri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:09.11,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,The detective's show of lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.73,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everyone will love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.30,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:20.35,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,you got into an argument with \Nsomeone near Suda-san's studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.58,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Paradise Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.19,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.19,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Paradise Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:35.39,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're DoDonPa\NRokusuke-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.65,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.57,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.49,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.96,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It happened just before 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You had art books then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,so you must have returned them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:55.60,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.97,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of other \Npeople who have art books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.86,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.10,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll know the truth once we check \Nthe prints on the art books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:10.56,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed them from her! \NOf course my prints are on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.57,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The fingerprints of the \Nman handing out tissues!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.24,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.75,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.05,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.64,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,He looked just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.90,DCItalic,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh. It's almost 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:43.24,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,His prints could only have gotten \Non the books when he picked them up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:46.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,after getting into an argument \Nwith you, DoDonPa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:50.63,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He visited Suda-san after their argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.38,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Not at 9:00, but at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:58.57,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,It's also unnatural for Suda-san to \Nsuddenly feel tired after eating cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.55,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After creating your false alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,you headed back to Beika City.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You left Beika Station at 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:15.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You made the metal bat appear \Nto be the murder weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and turned yourself in at \Nthe police station at 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After turning yourself in for the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:26.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,you waited for the real murder weapon \Nand your alibi witness to be found,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:31.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,so the police investigation \Nwould remove suspicion from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.04,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,You made us believe you were the suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:37.47,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,and then used us to clear you of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.78,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:44.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,He was trying to kill two\Nbirds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.96,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The press said
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:49.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,they learned you turned yourself\N in for President Tendo's murder
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,from an anonymous tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:57.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,However, at that time, the only person \Nwho could've release that information...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,is you, DoDonPa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.05,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:05.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,On your way to turn yourself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:10.35,DCItalic,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the comedian DoDonPa \NRokusuke-san turned himself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:15.73,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You told the reporters who \Ngathered your touching tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.22,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect the \Nreputation of Hideki Tendo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:23.24,DCItalic,ROKUSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I, DoDonPa Rokusuke, \Nwanted to be called his murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.78,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You used your unexpected confession
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.68,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,to make the world believe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:33.25,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,you were a good person and \Nbecome the center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.09,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Ding, ding, ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.01,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.86,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,The president was old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:49.14,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,He thought comedians should \Nonly put on comedy shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:53.52,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Entertainers want to rake in the cash \Ndoing anything they can, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.11,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I had him get out \Nof my way by disappearing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.90,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,while killing for two birds with \None stone, just like you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.78,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I got exactly what I wanted! \NThe jobs came pouring in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:09.22,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, my popularity's skyrocketing, \Nand I'm the man of the hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:17.09,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:21.49,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa never lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.05,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:33.81,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think a human life is worth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.32,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.34,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was really the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.76,DCMain,DODONPA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:23.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,DoDonPa doesn't lie? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:25.63,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:30.26,DCMain,SUGIMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Our machines pay out so much, \Nthey're begging our customers to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of lies, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Give 'em to me! Give me my balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:43.42,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A detective shouldn't fall \Nfor such obvious lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:24:09.00,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:46.48,DCMain,HIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Keigo Himura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:47.23,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:51.24,DCMain,HIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what they call a romance novel author.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:54.53,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, are you all right?! Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:57.24,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The clear resounding sound of this voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.19,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Minazuki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:15.01,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,The Romance Novel with the\NUnexpected Conclusion\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:10.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:15.01,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,“The Romance Novel with the\N Unexpected Conclusion, Part One!"
