Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:32.48,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.48,0:24:35.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Room service!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:37.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't read romance novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:40.36,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
